name: Degenerate
description: We are all Degens. The degen mentality existed long before the establishment of crypto, and it will exist long into the future. The Degen is a dreamer, an optimist, a believer and a hard worker. The memecoin space has historically dominated by it's most vocal and popular members, but the Degen finds strength in numbers. The $Degen token gives a voice to the silent majority of everyday traders who are just looking for a fair shot at a win. Together, the Degen in all traders will find that win.
